302
00:16:34,338 --> 00:16:36,538
from the amusement facility.

303
00:16:36,538 --> 00:16:38,838
Don't tell me you're saying that the culprit

304
00:16:38,838 --> 00:16:41,638
severed the band holding the pipes together from there?

305
00:16:41,638 --> 00:16:43,538
No way.

306
00:16:43,538 --> 00:16:46,038
Officer Chiba, please go ahead.

307
00:16:46,038 --> 00:16:47,538
Yes, sir.

308
00:16:47,538 --> 00:16:50,038
The culprit operated the breaker

309
00:16:50,038 --> 00:16:52,738
that is on the 1st floor of that building,

310
00:16:52,738 --> 00:16:55,038
made a certain something on the 2nd floor move

311
00:16:55,038 --> 00:16:57,338
