336
00:18:24,338 --> 00:18:26,138
You...

337
00:18:26,138 --> 00:18:28,838
I hope you have evidence to back up what you're saying.

338
00:18:28,838 --> 00:18:30,738
The evidence is your shoe.

339
00:18:30,738 --> 00:18:33,138
To be more exact, the sole of your shoe.

340
00:18:33,138 --> 00:18:35,738
Ran, show me the sole of your shoe.

341
00:18:35,738 --> 00:18:38,738
What? Mine?

342
00:18:40,438 --> 00:18:42,638
Okay.

343
00:18:42,638 --> 00:18:44,638
What's this red yarn?

344
00:18:44,638 --> 00:18:48,438
It's the yarn from the rug of the amusement facility, Funfun.

345
00:18:48,438 --> 00:18:50,038
If the same thing found on Ran's shoe

346
00:18:50,038 --> 00:18:51,838
is found on the sole of Mr. Murase's shoe,

347
00:18:51,838 --> 00:18:55,838
