393
00:21:22,538 --> 00:21:24,738
That's why I killed Inomata.

394
00:21:27,238 --> 00:21:28,838
Mr. Murase.

395
00:21:28,838 --> 00:21:31,838
It's not that I don't understand how you feel.

396
00:21:31,838 --> 00:21:34,138
However,

397
00:21:34,138 --> 00:21:38,538
just because he stepped all over your memories and crushed them,

398
00:21:38,538 --> 00:21:43,038
